mixin rating-input(id)
  .rating-input(data-rating-id=id)
    form.ally-rating(method="post" action="https://echo.htmlacademy.ru")
      label.ally-rating__label.visually-hidden(for="5_stars") Поставьте свою оценку (от 1 до 5)
      input.ally-rating__input.visually-hidden(type="number" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="inputRating")#5_stars
      .rating-5-stars
        .star(data-num-star="1")
        .star(data-num-star="2")
        .star(data-num-star="3")
        .star(data-num-star="4")
        .star(data-num-star="5")